codex
I’ve isolated the likely gap: the current verifier only works when the harness pre-seeds enough isolated collateral, and its bootstrap branch is a stub. I’m replacing that stub with an actual V2 flashswap funding path that buys isolated collateral, enters isolation mode, repeats the sub-unit borrows, repays the flash leg, and leaves any borrowed debt token surplus as realized profit.
